    "asOf": "2019-02-08",
    "date": "2022-01-13T15:19:01Z",
    "text": "Preventing Future Shutdowns Act of 2019\n\nThis bill provides continuing appropriations to prevent a government shutdown if any of the regular appropriations bills for a fiscal year have not been enacted before the fiscal year begins or a joint resolution making continuing appropriations is not in effect.\n\nIf appropriations have not been provided to federal agencies prior to the beginning of a fiscal year, the bill provides specified appropriations to continue programs, projects, and activities for which funds were provided in the preceding fiscal year."
  },
